      <title>股市下滑，华尔街迎来 GDP 警钟：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街对数据感到不安，这些数据恰恰显示了股票交易员不想听到的内容：全球最大经济体的显着放缓和持续的通胀压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 22:48:29 GMT</pubDate>
